14. Qxd3 Bc5+ 15. Kh1 (15. Kg2 Qxd3 16. cxd3 Rad8 $19) 15... Qxd3 16. cxd3 Rad8
17. Rf3 Rd5 18. Be3 $2 (18. Rb1 $19) 18... Rxd3 19. Bxc5 (19. Re1 {is not much
help} Nd5 20. Nf1 Rd8 $19) 19... Rxf3 20. Bxf8 Kxf8 21. Rd1 (21. f5 {doesn't
change the outcome of the game} exf5 22. Kg2 Rd3 23. Nxf5 Rd2+ 24. Kg1 Rxb2 $19
) 21... Ke7 (21... Rf2 $5 {keeps an even firmer grip} 22. b3 $19) 22. f5 Rf2
