(12... Bc8 $5 $11 {is worthy of consideration}) 13. Qc2 $14 b6 14. cxb6 cxb6
15. Bd2 Nc7 16. a4 Rc8 17. b3 (17. Ne5 Bb4 $16) 17... b5 18. Qb2 b4 {Black
