7. a3 {Secures b4} e5 (7... dxc4 $142 $5 {should be considered} 8. Bxc4 Bd6 $14
) 8. dxe5 $16 Ng4 9. cxd5 Ncxe5 10. Nc3 (10. Nxe5 Nxe5 11. f4 Ng6 $16) 10... a6
(10... Nxf3+ 11. Bxf3 f5 12. g3 $16) 11. Qc2 (11. Nd4 Nf6 12. e4 Bc5 $16) 11...
g6 (11... Nxf3+ 12. Bxf3 Bd6 13. g3 $16) 12. e4 (12. Nd4 c5 13. dxc6 Nxc6 14.
Nxc6 bxc6 $16) 12... c6 (12... Nxf3+ $5 13. gxf3 Nf6 $16) 13. h3 Nf6 $4 {
Black crumbles in face of a dire situation} (13... Nxf3+ $142 14. Bxf3 Ne5 $18)
14. Nxe5 Qd6 (14... cxd5 {the last chance for counterplay} 15. exd5 Nd7 16.
Nxd7 Bxd7 $18) 15. Bf4 cxd5 (15... Ne8 $18 {praying for a miracle}) 16. Nxg6 $1
{Discovered attack: e5, Bf4xd6} Qe6 (16... fxg6 17. Bxd6 {Discovered attack}) (
16... hxg6 17. Bxd6 {Discovered attack}) 17. exd5 (17. Nxe7+ {seems even better
} Qxe7 18. e5 Ne8 19. Nxd5 Qe6 $18) 17... Nxd5 (17... Qd7 {is no salvation} 18.
Nxf8 Bxf8 19. Na4 $18) 18. Nxf8 Bxf8 19. Bc4 (19. Nxd5 $142 {and White can
already relax} Qxd5 20. Rad1 $18) 19... Qc6 (19... Ne3 {doesn't get the bull
off the ice} 20. Bxe6 Nxc2 21. Bxc8 Rxc8 22. Rad1 $18) 20. Bxd5 (20. Nxd5 $142
{makes it even easier for White} Qg6 21. Qxg6+ hxg6 22. Nb6 $18) 20... Qc4 21.
Bxc4 Bd7 (21... Kh8 {doesn't change the outcome of the game} 22. Qe4 Bd7 23.
Nd5 Bg7 24. Nf6 Bxf6 25. Bd3 Bf5 26. Qxf5 Kg8 27. Bd6 Be7 28. Qxh7+ Kf8 29.
Qh8#) 22. Qd3 (22. Ne4 Be7 23. Qc3 Be6 24. Bh6 Bf8 25. Nf6+ Kh8 26. Qc2 Bf5 27.
