) 38... Kf7 (38... Rf8 $18 {otherwise it's curtains at once}) 39. Ke2 (39. Qxe4
Rh2+ 40. Kf3 Rh3+ 41. Kg2 Rhh8 42. Rxf5+ gxf5 43. Qxf5+ Ke7 44. Bxg7 Rhe8 45.
