{[%mdl 8256] B02: Alekhine's Defence: Chase Variation and lines with early Nc3
} 1. e4 d5 2. exd5 Nf6 3. Nc3 Bg4 (3... g6 4. Bc4 Bg7 5. Nge2 (5. d3 O-O 6. Nf3
Nbd7 7. O-O Nb6 8. Re1 Nfxd5 9. Nxd5 Nxd5 10. d4 c6 11. c3 Qd6 12. Qe2 Re8 13.
Ng5 b6 14. Qf3 Rf8 15. Bd2 f6 16. Ne4 Qd7 17. Rad1 Kh8 18. a4 a5 19. Qg3 Qg4 {
Ten Vergert,P (2194)-Wiegmann,S (2277) Germany 2012 1/2-1/2 (55)}) 5... O-O 6.
d3 Nbd7 7. Nf4 Nb6 8. Bb3 a5 9. a4 c6 10. dxc6 e5 11. Nfe2 bxc6 12. O-O Nbd5
13. Ne4 h6 14. Nxf6+ Qxf6 15. Bd2 Qd8 16. Nc3 Kh7 17. Qf3 Be6 18. Rfe1 {
