$146 (5. Qxe2 Nbd7 (5... Nxd5 6. Qb5+ c6 7. Qxb7 Qb6 8. Qc8+ Qd8 9. Qxd8+ Kxd8
10. Nxd5 cxd5 11. Nf3 Nc6 12. O-O f6 13. d4 e6 14. Be3 Bd6 15. Rac1 Rc8 16. c4
Kd7 17. c5 Bc7 18. Rfd1 Rb8 19. Rb1 Rb7 20. Ne1 {Le,K (2341)-Chau Thi Ngoc,G 
(2182) Dalat City 2004 1/2-1/2 (45)}) 6. d4 Nb6 7. Qb5+ Qd7 8. Qxd7+ Kxd7 9.
Nf3 Nbxd5 10. Nxd5 Nxd5 11. c4 Nb4 12. O-O e6 13. Rd1 f6 14. a3 Na6 15. b4 c6
16. Nd2 Nc7 17. Ne4 Be7 18. Bf4 b6 19. Rac1 g5 {Varga,S (2260)-Donka,P (2270)
Hungary 1995 1-0 (52)}) 5... Nxd5 6. O-O Nc6 7. d3 e5 8. Nxd5 Qxd5 {White has
a cramped position} 9. Nc3 {White threatens to win material: Nc3xd5} Qd7 10.
Bg5 f6 {Black threatens to win material: f6xg5} 11. Bh4 (11. Be3 O-O-O $11)
11... O-O-O {Black castles and improves king safety} 12. Ne4 (12. f3 Bc5+ 13.
Bf2 Bxf2+ 14. Rxf2 Kb8 $15) 12... Be7 $17 13. Bg3 $2 (13. f3 $142 $17) 13... f5
$19 14. Nd2 f4 15. Bxf4 exf4 16. Qf3 g5 17. Rfe1 (17. Qh5 Kb8 $19) 17... Nd4 (
17... Bb4 $142 {and Black can already relax} 18. c3 Qxd3 19. Qg4+ Kb8 $19) 18.
Qe4 (18. Qd1 $19) 18... Nxc2 19. Qxe7 Qxe7 20. Rxe7 Nxa1 21. Re1 (21. Ne4 {
does not save the day} h6 $19) 21... Rxd3 22. Nf1 (22. Ne4 {doesn't get the
cat off the tree} Nc2 23. Rb1 Rhd8 $19) 22... Nc2 23. Re5 (23. Re4 {does not
help much} Kd7 $19) 23... Nd4 24. h3 (24. Re7 {is not much help} Kd8 25. Re1
Kd7 $19) 24... Rd1 25. f3 Nc2 26. Kf2 Rhd8 27. g3 Ne3 $1 {Deflection: d2} 28.
Nxe3 (28. Nxe3 R8d2# {Mate attack Interception Deflection}) (28. Z0 $140 Rxf1+
{Mate threat}) 28... R8d2# 0-1

