White king safety dropped} (26... Qh4 27. Rf3 $15) 27. Rd1 $11 Reg8 28. Rf3 {
White threatens to win material: Rf3xe3} Qh6 29. Qg4 Rf8 30. Rd2 Bc8 {Black
threatens to win material: Bc8xg4} 31. Qg3 g5 32. Rdf2 Qg7 (32... Rxf3 33. Rxf3
g4 34. Rf4 $11) 33. Rxf8 $14 Rxf8 34. Rxf8 Qxf8 35. Qxg5 {White has a new
