Qe2 a5 38. a3 Ka7 39. Qb5 (39. g4 $5 $16) 39... Qf2+ $11 {Black forks: g2} 40.
Qe2 {White threatens to win material: Qe2xf2} Qc5 {Twofold repetition} 41. Qf3
