O-O d6 10. Qe2 Ne4 11. Be1 Nd7 12. Rc1 Ndf6 13. Nd2 Nxc3 14. Rxc3 Ne4 15. Rc1
Bf6 16. Nxe4 fxe4 17. Bb1 d5 18. c5 a5 19. b4 c6 20. Qg4 Bc8 21. Qh5 Ba6 {
Ushakova,I (2182)-Ivanov,J (2382) Riazan 2007 0-1 (46)}) 7... Bxc3 8. Bxc3 Ne4
9. Rc1 d6 10. Bg2 Nd7 11. d5 Nxc3 12. Rxc3 e5 13. e4 fxe4 14. Nd2 Nf6 15. Nxe4
O-O 16. O-O Qe7 17. Ng5 Bc8 18. f4 Bg4 19. Bf3 Bd7 20. Re3 {Yanchenko,R (2384)
-Pridorozhni,A (2569) Vladivostok 2015 0-1 (75)}) 6. Bd3 $4 {releasing the
pressure on the opponent} (6. f3 $142 $11 {would bring relief}) 6... Bxc3 (6...
Bxg2 $142 {makes it even easier for Black} 7. Nce2 Bxd2+ 8. Kxd2 Bxh1 9. f3 $19
) 7. Bxc3 Bxg2 8. Nf3 (8. f3 {hoping against hope} Bxh1 9. Qe2 $19) 8... Bxh1
9. Kd2 Bxf3 10. Qxf3 d5 11. Rg1 g6 12. Qf4 (12. Kc2 {cannot undo what has
already been done} c6 $19) 12... Ne4+ (12... Nbd7 $142 {and Black wins} 13. c5
$19) 13. Bxe4 dxe4 14. Qxe4 Nd7 15. d5 (15. Ke2 $19 {doesn't get the cat off
the tree}) 15... f5 (15... O-O $142 $19 {and Black has it in the bag}) 16.
Qxe6+ $11 Qe7 17. Bxh8 Qxe6 18. dxe6 Nc5 19. Bf6 $4 {not a good decision,
because now the opponent is right back in the game} (19. Ke2 $142 $11 {was
necessary}) 19... Ne4+ $19 20. Kd3 Nxf6 21. Kd4 (21. Ke2 {does not win a prize}
Rd8 $19) 21... Ke7 (21... Rd8+ {seems even better} 22. Kc3 Ne4+ 23. Kb3 Rd3+
24. Ka4 Nxf2 25. Kb5 Rxe3 26. h4 $19) 22. Ke5 (22. f3 {doesn't do any good}
Kxe6 23. b3 Rd8+ 24. Kc3 f4 $19) 22... Ng4+ 23. Kf4 (23. Kd5 {cannot change
destiny} Rd8+ 24. Kc6 Rd2 $19) 23... Kxe6 (23... Nxf2 $142 $5 {keeps an even
firmer grip} 24. Kf3 Nd3 25. b3 $19) 24. e4 Nxf2 25. exf5+ gxf5 26. Rg7 Nd3+
27. Kg5 (27. Kf3 {cannot change what is in store for White} Nxb2 28. Rxc7 h5
$19) 27... f4 (27... Rf8 28. Kh4 f4 29. Rg1 Nxb2 30. Re1+ Kf5 31. Kh3 $19) 28.
Kg4 Rf8 29. Kf3 Nxb2 30. Rxh7 (30. Rxc7 {desperation} Rf7 31. Rc8 $19) 30...
Nxc4 31. Rh6+ Kf5 32. Rh5+ Kg6 33. Rd5 c5 (33... Rf5 $142 {might be the
shorter path} 34. Rd1 $19) 34. h4 (34. h3 {doesn't change anything anymore} Rf5
35. Rd1 Ne5+ 36. Ke4 f3 $19) 34... Rf5 35. Rd8 (35. Rd1 {is not the saving move
} Ne5+ 36. Kg2 Rh5 $19) 35... Ne5+ 36. Kf2 f3 37. Rg8+ Kf7 38. Rg3 c4 (38...
Nd3+ 39. Kg1 c4 40. Rg4 c3 41. Rc4 Rc5 42. Rd4 c2 43. Rd7+ Ke6 44. Rxd3 c1=Q+
45. Kf2 Qc2+ 46. Kxf3 Qxd3+ 47. Kg4 Rf5 48. h5 Qf3+ 49. Kh4 Rxh5#) 39. Rg5 Rxg5
40. hxg5 (40. Ke3 {doesn't change the outcome of the game} Rg4 41. a4 c3 42. a5
