Bar 1977 1/2-1/2 (56)}) 10... a6 {Prevents intrusion on b5} (10... Ne4 11. Re1
$11) 11. a3 {White has an active position} Qc7 (11... Bg4 12. h3 Bxf3 13. Bxf3
$11) 12. Bf4 $14 e5 $2 (12... Qd8 $142 $5 $14 {and Black can hope to survive})
13. Nxe5 (13. dxe5 $142 Nh5 14. Nxd5 $18) 13... Ne4 $4 {Black has lost his
nerve... understandable when you consider his position} (13... Qd8 $142 $16)
14. Nxg6 $1 {Discovered attack: e5, Bf4xc7} Qd8 (14... fxg6 15. Bxc7 {
Discovered attack}) (14... hxg6 15. Bxc7 {Discovered attack}) 15. Nxf8 Nxc3 (
15... Kxf8 {does not save the day} 16. Nxe4 dxe4 17. d5 $18) 16. bxc3 Bxf8 (
16... Qxf8 {cannot undo what has already been done} 17. Bxd5 Be6 18. Bd6 $18)
17. Qb3 Na5 (17... Qf6 {doesn't get the bull off the ice} 18. Qxd5 h6 19. Rfe1
$18) 18. Qxd5 Be6 (18... Bd7 {doesn't change the outcome of the game} 19. Rfb1
Bg7 20. Be4 $18) 19. Qg5+ (19. Qxd8 $142 {and White has prevailed} Rxd8 20. Bc7
Nc6 21. Bxd8 Nxd8 $18) 19... Qxg5 20. Bxg5 h6 (20... Bd7 {is not the saving
move} 21. Rfe1 $18) 21. Bf4 Rd8 (21... Bf5 {a fruitless try to alter the
course of the game} 22. Bc7 Nc6 23. d5 Bxc5 24. dxc6 bxc6 25. Bf4 $18) 22. Bc7
Rd7 (22... Nc6 {doesn't change anything anymore} 23. Bxd8 Nxd8 24. Rfb1 $18)
23. Bxa5 Be7 24. Rab1 Bc4 25. Rfe1 b5 26. cxb6 (26. c6 Ra7 27. Bb6 Rc7 28. Bxc7
Bd3 29. Rxe7 h5 30. Be5 Kh7 31. c7 Bf5 32. Rxf7+ Kg6 33. Rf6+ Kg7 34. Rxf5+ Kh7
35. c8=Q Kg6 36. Qe6+ Kh7 37. Rxh5#) 26... Bd6 27. Re8+ Kg7 28. b7 Bb5 29. b8=Q
